%p.sg-p This project uses a sticky footer technique insipred by this <a href="http://pixelsvsbytes.com/blog/2011/09/sticky-css-footers-the-flexible-way/" class="sg-a" target="_blank">article</a>. To implement it, apply the <span class="sg-code">.sticky-wrapper</span> class to the body. Wrap all the content except the site's footer in a div with the class <span class="sg-code">.sticky-main</span> and apply the <span class="sg-code">.sticky-footer</span> class to the site's footer.
